FSP CMT192 RGB ATX Gaming Case

The FSP CMT192 RGB ATX Gaming Case is a stylish and spacious gaming case that can accommodate ATX, Micro ATX, and Mini-ITX motherboards. It has a tempered glass side panel that showcases your components and RGB lighting effects. It comes with four 120mm fixed RGB fans, three in the front and one in the rear, that create a stunning airflow and illumination. The FSP CMT192 RGB ATX Gaming Case also supports up to two 140mm fans in the front and two 120mm fans in the top for additional cooling options. You can also install up to a 240-mm radiator in the front or top for liquid cooling. The FSP CMT192 RGB has enough room for a 160mm CPU cooler and a 285mm VGA card, as well as two 3.5" HDDs (shared with SSD) and one 2.5" SSD for storage. It has a convenient I/O panel on the top, with one USB 3.0 port, two USB 2.0 ports, and audio jacks. The FSP CMT192 RGB ATX Gaming Case is 350x200x437mm in size and features a stylish and reliable SPCC construction.
